OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FDozens of schools have been forced to
OL,8,Fclose and transport bosses have warned
OL,9,Fpeople against all but essential
OL,10,Ftravel amid rare red warnings over
OL,11,Fextreme temperatures that are expected
OL,12,Fto hit record highs for June.
OL,14,FA "heat-dome" settling over western
OL,15,FEurope could bring temperatures of up
OL,16,Fto 40C in some parts of England and
OL,17,FWales in the middle part of the week,
OL,18,Fthe Met Office has said.
OL,26,@vD@COUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
