OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FTemperatures for the latest heatwave
OL,8,Fare likely to overtake the June record
OL,9,Fset in Hampshire in 1976 by several
OL,10,Fdegrees and could come close to the
OL,11,FUK's all-time high of 40.3C which was
OL,12,Fmeasured in July 2022.
OL,14,FThe hot conditions, which have been
OL,15,Fvery rare in the UK until now, will be
OL,16,Faccompanied by high humidity and very
OL,17,Fwarm nights, which will make it hard
OL,18,Ffor people to recover overnight, the
OL,19,Fforecaster warned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
