OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FA red weather warning for extreme heat
OL,8,Fcovering an area stretching from
OL,9,FLondon to Swansea and Somerset to
OL,10,FBirmingham was issued by the Met
OL,11,FOffice from 9am on Wednesday to 9pm on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FThese are reserved for the most severe
OL,15,Fevents, the Met Office said, meaning
OL,16,Fthis heatwave is expected to bring
OL,17,F"severe and significant impacts"
OL,18,Fincluding widespread health risks for
OL,19,Fmany, not just those who are normally
OL,20,Fmore vulnerable to the heat, and even
OL,21,Fdanger to life.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@`O]
