OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FScores of schools across England and
OL,8,FWales announced they would close or
OL,9,Ffinish early later this week to
OL,10,Fprotect pupils amid the extreme heat.
OL,12,FThe Buckingham School in
OL,13,FBuckinghamshire said it will be closed
OL,14,Fon Wednesday and Thursday, and asked
OL,15,Fstudents to take part in online
OL,16,Flearning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
