CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782209900
OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FIn a statement on its website on
OL,8,FMonday, the school said: "Because most
OL,9,Fof our buildings cannot be cooled
OL,10,Fadequately and there is little shade
OL,11,Foutside, we have taken the difficult
OL,12,Fdecision to close the school site on
OL,13,Fboth days (Wednesday and Thursday).
OL,15,F"All trips and other scheduled
OL,16,Factivities are also cancelled."
OL,18,FThe school, which has around 1,200
OL,19,Fstudents until sixth form, said
OL,20,Fteachers will upload work online for
OL,21,Fpupils to complete.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUwD@AOUxD@_O]
