OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FSt John's Marlborough in Wiltshire
OL,8,Fsaid it will close early on Tuesday
OL,9,Fand be shut all day on Wednesday and
OL,10,FThursday before re-opening on Friday.
OL,12,FThe Dorcan Academy in Swindon,
OL,13,FWiltshire, said on-site learning will
OL,14,Ffinish at 11.30am on Tuesday and the
OL,15,Fschool will remain closed on Wednesday
OL,16,Fand Thursday.
OL,18,FOther schools in Sutton in south
OL,19,FLondon and Haringey in north London
OL,20,Fhave also been forced to close from
OL,21,FTuesday to Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
