OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FSome schools will remain open this
OL,8,Fweek but close at about lunchtime on
OL,9,FTuesday, Wednesday and Thursday,
OL,10,Fincluding Pewsey Vale School, Dilton
OL,11,FMarsh Primary and Malmesbury School in
OL,12,FWiltshire, Ditton Park Academy in
OL,13,FSlough, Berkshire, The Bulmershe
OL,14,FSchool in Reading, Berkshire, Cheam
OL,15,FHigh School in Surrey and Sydenham
OL,16,FSchool in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
