OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the National Association of
OL,8,FHead Teachers (NAHT) said it has
OL,9,Fwritten to all its members with
OL,10,Fguidance on dealing with the heat this
OL,11,Fweek, including the impact on pupils
OL,12,Fand staff, legal positions and when to
OL,13,Fconsider closure.
OL,15,FPaul Whiteman, NAHT general secretary,
OL,16,Fsaid: "While there is no legal 'upper
OL,17,Flimit' for temperature in schools,
OL,18,F(school leaders) will certainly be
OL,19,Fdoing all they can to mitigate the
OL,20,Feffects of such high temperatures."
OL,26,@xD@GOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
