OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FAdvice has also been issued for
OL,8,Ftransport users, with Network Rail
OL,9,Fwarning passengers should "only travel
OL,10,Fif absolutely essential on Wednesday
OL,11,Fand Thursday".
OL,13,FJake Kelly, deputy chief executive of
OL,14,FNetwork Rail, said: "Extreme heat can
OL,15,Fhave a significant impact on the
OL,16,Frailway, so safety must come first.
OL,26,@qD@[OUsD@MO]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782209900
OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,F"We're asking passengers to check
OL,8,Fbefore travelling on Tuesday, and only
OL,9,Ftravel if absolutely essential on
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday if they are
OL,11,Fgoing to, from or within the red
OL,12,Fwarning zone as temperatures are
OL,13,Fexpected to peak.
OL,15,F"If you do need to travel in this area
OL,16,For outside of it where it will still
OL,17,Fbe hot, please plan ahead, allow extra
OL,18,Ftime and take necessary precautions,
OL,19,Fsuch as carrying water, to stay safe.
OL,20,FWe thank passengers for their patience
OL,21,Fand understanding during this period."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU}D@fO]
