OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fhas issued a red health warning for
OL,9,Fsix regions of England ` the West
OL,10,FMidlands, East Midlands, South East,
OL,11,FSouth West, London, and east of
OL,12,FEngland ` from 1am on Wednesday until
OL,13,F11pm on Thursday.
OL,15,FThis indicates "a risk to life for
OL,16,Feven the healthy population" as well
OL,17,Fas impacts beyond health and social
OL,18,Fcare, with potential effects on
OL,19,Ftransport systems, food, water, energy
OL,20,Fsupplies and businesses.
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
