OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FTransport for London (TfL) warned
OL,8,Fcustomers of possible disruption to
OL,9,Frail and Tube services, saying rail
OL,10,Ftemperatures could lead to temporary
OL,11,Fspeed restrictions and reduced
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782209900
OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FClaire Mann, TfL's chief operating
OL,8,Fofficer, said: "Customers should be
OL,9,Faware that, given the very high
OL,10,Ftemperatures that are forecast, we are
OL,11,Flikely to see some disruption to rail
OL,12,Fand Tube services ` with rail
OL,13,Ftemperatures likely to lead to
OL,14,Ftemporary speed restrictions and
OL,15,Ftherefore reduced services in some
OL,16,Fcases.
OL,26,@pD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
