CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782209900
OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,F"This will vary by line, with some
OL,8,Fservices that share parts of the
OL,9,Foverground rail network ` like the
OL,10,FOverground and the Elizabeth line `
OL,11,Flikely to be more affected."
OL,13,FShe added: "We expect bus services to
OL,14,Frun as normal although, during periods
OL,15,Fof hot weather, we are encouraging
OL,16,Fcustomers to carry water with them
OL,17,Fwhen they travel on any of our
OL,18,Fservices."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@\O]uD@LOUzD@JO]
