OL,3,CDozens of schools to close amid
OL,4,Cimpending rare red warnings for
OL,5,Cextreme heat
OL,7,FThe AA said drivers could also see
OL,8,Fgritters out on some roads this week
OL,9,Fwith the potential for surfaces to
OL,10,Fsoften or become sticky under the
OL,11,Fheat, with heavy traffic even causing
OL,12,Fthem to rut in some places.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
